channel.title: WishScape - made by peoples favorate pk maker
channel.description:
[center]WishScape[/center]
Me and Dale decided too give a non-pk ago... Well we came up with WishScape :eek: Heres some future updates and some whitch are done in v.1 :-)
Already done: barrows shop rune shop prayer shop dragon armour/some weps shop dragon weps shop random item shop rare shop Working duel area changed everything from project to WishScape.
Coming soon in v.1:
For all: ::hoilday - gives all phats ::mime - gives full mime ::camo - gives full camo ::crazywoody - gives full lerdonhosen ::froggym - gives full frog prince ::froggyf - gives full frog princess ::poor - gives 100mill ::train - teles you too a training zone. ::protrain - teles you too high level training zone.
Mods only: ::kick - kicks a player ::modisland - teles them too a mod island ::moduniform - gives them the mod uniform
Admins only: ::giveadmin [playername] - ... ::givemod [playername] -... ::adminisland - teles them to a island ::xteleto [playername] ::xteletome [playername]
this is only v.2, also post some stuff you want. :-)
